    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The validation evidence, including R-squared of 0.97, Pearson correlation of 0.985, and RMSE of 0.0031 mg/100 mL, is judged to demonstrate sufficient model fidelity for the CPB hemolysis prediction task. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
